Bach Viewer unit tests
======================

Viewer unit tests has been written on the top of atoum (http://atoum.org/).

Execute unit tests running the following:
$ php vendor/atoum/atoum/bin/atoum  -bf tests/Bootstrap.php -d tests/Bach

This will execute all available tests.

If you want to generate coevrage report, simply add
"-c tests/config/coverage.php" at the end of the command.
This way, coverage informations will be created in tests-results/coverage directory.

Please read atoum documentation at http://docs.atoum.org/ if you want
to learn more.
